description: Page is a pet parrot of Mr. Saitou, http://anidb.net/ch4068 [Yukio]`s guitar teacher. Page always sings along with Mr.Saitou`s favourite band, but never when Mr.Saitou plays the guitar, which frustrates him to no end. So, Mr. Saitou and Yukio decide that they will practice until they are good enough to make Page sing.
name: Page
